{"word":"γενειάς","slug":"γενειάς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γενειάς</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γένειον'><el>γένειον</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a beard</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>the sides of the face, cheeks</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}